data.description: Investors and First time homebuyers…this is your GOLDEN TICKET!  This open concept home has recently been remodeled and hosts three spacious bedrooms, each with their own full bathroom and an additional 1/2 bath to boot. The master bath features a shower and separate soaking tub and double vanities . This split floorplan is situated on a peaceful cul de sac within short distance to local amenities. This one won’t last…get your showing TODAY!
